data.description: Look - $5000 Price Improvement! You don't want to miss the chance to make this your next home! Located in Sugarmill Woods in Cypress Village. This Beautiful 4 bedroom, 3 full bathroom, 3 car garage home sits on a corner lot with a circular driveway. Enter through the Double Doors and be blown away by the impeccable engineered hardwood floors featured throughout the home. This split floorplan offers privacy for your guests.  The 4th bedroom is located in the front of the home, and may be used as an office or work out room. There are two master bedrooms. The Main Master is spacious with ample closet space and storage & has triple sliding glass doors that lead right out to the back lanai where you could drink your morning coffee and watch the cranes walk by. The bathrooms feature ceramic tile floors. The screened in lanai, roof and air conditioning unit were all updated in 2020!!! Kitchen appliances were upgraded in 2022 to Black Stainless Steel. The backyard is ready to put in your dream pool! Come check it out today and make this paradise your forever home !!
